# game/Locations/gym.rpy:40
translate spanish gym_36e0a910:

    # "I drive past the Boxing Club, but there's a bunch of tough looking guys standing out front."
    "Paso en coche por delante del club de boxeo, pero hay un grupo de tipos de aspecto rudo delante de la entrada."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:41
translate spanish gym_ef6cbc94:

    # "They're not going to let me in without Tammy."
    "No me van a dejar entrar sin Tammy."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:42
translate spanish gym_d0ea8332:

    # "She says that she works out in the afternoons. I should come back then."
    "Ella dice que entrena por las tardes. Debería volver entonces."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:45
translate spanish gym_6ea3bd27:

    # "The gym is closed right now. I should come back tomorrow."
    "El gimnasio está cerrado ahora mismo. Debería volver mañana."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:53
translate spanish gymmenu_edf16bd3:

    # "I don't think I could work out any more today. I'm still feeling a little sore from earlier."
    "No creo que pueda entrenar más hoy. Todavía me duele un poco de antes."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:58
translate spanish workoutsolo_3a637c54:

    # "I decide to spend some time lifting weights."
    "Decido dedicar un rato a levantar pesas."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:59
translate spanish workoutsolo_e8858a0a:

    # "I push myself as far as I can, focusing on my movements and building the muscles."
    "Me exijo al máximo, centrándome en los movimientos y en desarrollar los músculos."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:63
translate spanish workoutsolo_3cafae02:

    # "I'm not sure I could get much stronger than I already am with these exercises."
    "No estoy seguro de poder hacerme mucho más fuerte de lo que ya soy con estos ejercicios."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:67
translate spanish workoutsolo_43573581:

    # "When I finished, I'm covered in a sheen of sweat and my muscles are burning, but in a good way."
    "Cuando termino, estoy cubierto de una capa de sudor y me arden los músculos, pero en el buen sentido."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:68
translate spanish workoutsolo_0a1ce5ce:

    # "I head to the showers and clean off quickly, then wave goodbye to some of the other guys as I walk back out to my car."
    "Me dirijo a las duchas y me aseo rápidamente, luego me despido de algunos de los otros chicos mientras salgo hacia mi coche."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:71
translate spanish workoutsolo_cdda925e:

    # "It's almost time for school. I quickly get in my car and drive."
    "Ya casi es hora de ir al colegio. Me subo rápidamente al coche y conduzco."

# game/Locations/gym.rpy:80
translate spanish workoutsolo_9feb0d61:

    # "I don't really need to be here right now."
    "En realidad no necesito estar aquí ahora mismo."

